Klopp on Man City: &quot;I don't think it was a good day for football, yesterday. I think FFP is a good idea for protecting competition.&quot;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &quot;It's not up to me to judge this and I don't. I only think this FFP frame, we all should stick to. I really hope that FFP stays because it gives borders where you can go to but not over it and I think that's good for football.&quot;
